Notes

--derep_fulllength identifies sequences identical across their entire length.

--sizeout appends ;size=N; to indicate the abundance of each sequence.

--relabel renames sequences with a unique sample-specific prefix.

The output files are stored in ../Dereplicated/ for downstream analyses like taxonomic classification (e.g., using EMU).
